{"tid":1992752,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"《是咁的，我係一個化妝女神，素顏豬扒。》1","createTime":"2020-04-28T10:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T05:36:59.000Z","uid":202541,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a478817b02611ab3c8b402e742c39bb7f7013e9e","tid":1992752,"uid":202541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:36:07.000Z","msg":"愛靚係女人天性，包括我在內。但無奈，天俾咗個唔好嘅首抽我。你問我會點形容自己？眼唔大唔細，鼻又唔高唔矮咁囉，一句講哂就係比上不足 比下有餘。<br />\n<br />\n我嘅中小學讀書生涯同邊緣人畫上等號，醜、豬扒、極品，從來圍繞我身邊嘅形容詞，一隻手都數得哂。點解個樣好似正正常常咁都會有人咁講我？因為我唔止唔靚，我仲係一個好深近視嘅四眼妹啊！<br />\n<br />\n500度近視，粗框黑色眼鏡令我對眼睇落更細，完美咁令我醜上加醜。<br />\n<br />\n煲劇，係我人生中嘅最大興趣，因為戲劇世界入面，一切都有可能。咩醜小鴨變白天鵝，灰姑娘搖身一變做公主look，我真係以為隨時間流逝我就會變靚㗎。睇住《命中注定我愛你》陳喬恩原本由一個普通平凡嘅女仔，去到遇上阮經天變做一個超級大靚女<br />\n<br />\n「哇屌，差咁撚多嘅？」我食住薯片屌出聲。<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣好興睇台劇啊台綜乜乜乜咁，身為一個邊緣人，冇人約咪煲下劇囉。啊，唔煲又至好，一煲就上哂腦，日煲夜煲，完全停唔到。尤其係嗰啲叫人上節目落妝嘅低能節目，我又睇得好撚入迷。點解對眼可以差成倍大？點解啲皮膚咁差都可以睇落咁白滑？點解點解點解點解點解。<br />\n<br />\n就係咁，我嗰日就去咗格仔鋪買咗人生第一對大眼仔。順手買咗枝有色潤唇膏同眼線筆，打算返屋企睇下變唔變到陳喬恩。"},{"pid":"cc453ab48d05314513663c534ea24edfc3b731c1","tid":1992752,"uid":83440,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddeb5651a26587b17a3144fac788c20a93260aed","tid":1992752,"uid":202541,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:21:19.000Z","msg":"「哇哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈～！！！」<br />\n「佢咩事啊屌哈哈哈哈。」<br />\n「佢做咩化到成個小丑咁？」<br />\n我專登一早起身用咗成個鐘化嘅妝，換嚟嘅係全班人嘅嘲笑，我嗰下真係好想搵窿捐。<br />\n（化妝失敗示意圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iiGjePK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiiGjePK.jpg&h=39b8d43d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n返到學校前我都一路FF緊個妝有冇令我好睇啲，啲人會唔會覺得我靚咗，真係唔需要太多，我只想有變好少少，少少都夠。可惜事與願違。我成個小息都將自己鎖係廁所，喊足成個小息，直至眼又腫又痛。<br />\n<br />\n「到底我係為咩而咁樣委屈自己？點解我要咁蠢？我到底做錯咗啲咩？」我一路自言自語咁用力洗走面上嘅小丑妝。<br />\n<br />\n終於，我捱到暑假。<br />\n<br />\n我用咗成個暑假去鑽研化妝，去書店買咩化妝入門技巧，喪睇美妝Youtuber。最後我用咗成個月零用錢去買化妝品，努力練習去做一個世俗眼中嘅正常人，起碼都要擺脫豬扒呢個名。<br />\n<br />\n日子一日一日咁過，好怕到9月1號又要返學。不過好彩，今年我調咗班。面對嘅係一班完全唔同嘅人，我諗應該會好啲掛。起碼可能會識到朋友唔使再做邊緣人掛。<br />\n<br />\n第一日開學，我太過緊張係咁修輯自己個妝，一唔小心就搞到遲到。心諗：唉屌，錯過咗個識fd最佳時機。<br />\n<br />\n一行入課室，原本嘈亂巴閉嘅課室突然之間靜哂。<br />\n<br />\n（仆街，睇嚟個妝又炒咗車。嗚，睇黎又要做毒撚一個人食飯。）<br />\n<br />\n全班得返一個空位，我好自然咁坐咗落去。隔嚟位係個女仔，睇落都似化咗妝，上咗粉底、遮瑕、眉、少少眼影同唇膏。整體嚟講都幾靚女，眼大大皮膚又好，真係好想知佢枝唇膏係咩色號，點解咁好睇。<br />\n<br />\n「我叫啊珊啊，你呢？」佢笑住聊我講野。<br />\n<br />\n唔係講笑，嗰下我個心跳得快過將軍令。佢眼大笑容甜把聲又溫柔，笑起上嚟仲有兩個酒粒，身為女人我都覺得好正&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n「我&hellip;&hellip;我叫啊恬啊，你好啊。」今日係我人生中第一次有人主動聊我講野。心諗呢個世界點解會有啲咁完美嘅女人，樣靚人又好。<br />\n<br />\n「你個妝化得好好睇呀啊恬，你得閒可唔可以教下我啊？我好鍾意你個眼妝啊！」<br />\n<br />\n我分唔清佢係講緊笑定係客套說話定其實佢想兜個圈嚟笑我。<br />\n<br />\n「係咩&hellip;&hellip;哈哈，唔似小丑咩？」<br />\n<br />\n「吓？咩小丑啊？頭先你一入嚟就成班人靜哂。個個男仔都望住你喎，鬼唔知你靚咩，仲扮謙虛。」佢笑住講。<br />\n<br />\n第一次俾人話靚，第一次有人主動聊我傾偈，對像仲要係一個靚女。我真係覺得佢個頭上面有個光頭，佢唔應該係地上出現，應該係天使。就係咁，我中學校園生活識到第一個朋友，仲要係個靚女，嗰陣我嘅心情仲開心過生日。"},{"pid":"37cf21dcfa13b94380aea7826f5dc57672803db9","tid":1992752,"uid":161174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:58:24.000Z","msg":"你好認真，我應該俾正皮定負皮你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6374ebbadc40275642faf2f7eb27e8f8b80908b","tid":1992752,"uid":161174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:59:10.000Z","msg":"頭上面有個光頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae44a06e2f4e88e3d20c80641a4342c3b687ae3","tid":1992752,"uid":237795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6374ebbadc40275642faf2f7eb27e8f8b80908b","tid":1992752,"uid":161174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:59:10.000Z","msg":"頭上面有個光頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5398f248f80cba74b192866ff8c8ec610399e610","tid":1992752,"uid":298118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6374ebbadc40275642faf2f7eb27e8f8b80908b","tid":1992752,"uid":161174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:59:10.000Z","msg":"頭上面有個光頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T15:24:25.000Z","msg":"屌笑到停唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原本睇唔到<br />\nBut個故幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075baf581bf73d9bb536ab566d961c70b8ba16cc","tid":1992752,"uid":83440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T15:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7160978e0a988dc0058e875e9b58a5f33f8477f5","tid":1992752,"uid":202541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6374ebbadc40275642faf2f7eb27e8f8b80908b","tid":1992752,"uid":161174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:59:10.000Z","msg":"頭上面有個光頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T17:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都冇發現"},{"pid":"e52f795ddd7f44dc248ed50d66a214fa2eb8da10","tid":1992752,"uid":202541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37cf21dcfa13b94380aea7826f5dc57672803db9","tid":1992752,"uid":161174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:58:24.000Z","msg":"你好認真，我應該俾正皮定負皮你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T17:25:08.000Z","msg":"認真地打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5589dc4f2c793a2b6fe7895cecd21a9b5296ecf9","tid":1992752,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e52f795ddd7f44dc248ed50d66a214fa2eb8da10","tid":1992752,"uid":202541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37cf21dcfa13b94380aea7826f5dc57672803db9","tid":1992752,"uid":161174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:58:24.000Z","msg":"你好認真，我應該俾正皮定負皮你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T17:25:08.000Z","msg":"認真地打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"已正皮，加油"},{"pid":"dc5eb03bc3368fa521750b7d9b11e8e563d76cda","tid":1992752,"uid":174432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T17:28:41.000Z","msg":"想問下幾耐會出一次文？<br />\n個題材都幾吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609f4b7a298f81d9fe3a6c15d834a0a0184cc24a","tid":1992752,"uid":202541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc5eb03bc3368fa521750b7d9b11e8e563d76cda","tid":1992752,"uid":174432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T17:28:41.000Z","msg":"想問下幾耐會出一次文？<br />\n個題材都幾吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T17:31:17.000Z","msg":"得閒就出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98560b2dd2cd21282002e5bcd65e26a6df8e98e","tid":1992752,"uid":202541,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:48:35.000Z","msg":"（男廁兩個尿兜前）<br />\n<br />\n「估唔到今年同咁多靚女同班，坐前排嗰兩個女仔都好靚，原來靚女都係同返靚女玩。」黃浩然屙住尿講。<br />\n<br />\n「右邊嗰條女正撚到呢，個樣又淫又西面。唔知佢仲係咪處呢，想私有化佢之後日日砌，好想瘋狂中出佢啊屌！」<br />\n<br />\n「喂你咁講野嘅？你當人地係咩？」<br />\n<br />\n「我唔理，我今個月就要溝到呢條女日日砌，我陳浚軒講嘅！」<br />\n<br />\n「痴撚線。」浩然西住面拉起褲鏈行去洗手。<br />\n <br />\n/<br />\n<br />\n估唔到啊珊同我會咁啱傾，同佢傾咗成半個小息都好似唔係傾咗好耐咁，我地下至戴咩CON，上至用咩M巾都可以同對方分享，呢種girl&rsquo;s talk，係我以前從來唔敢幻想。突然無啦啦有個男仔行埋嚟打斷咗我地嘅對話。<br />\n<br />\n「Hello，兩位靚女，我叫陳浚軒。唔知兩位會唔會可以俾我抄個牌，等我add你地入WhatsApp班群呢？」<br />\n<br />\n「唔見你問其他人拎電話嘅？」啊珊語氣突然變得好冷漠，好似唔見咗個光環咁惡。<br />\n<br />\n「咁啱你地你第一個啫，唔使咁緊張喎。」佢皮笑肉不笑咁答。<br />\n<br />\n「唔緊要啦，我俾你啦。」我見氣氛咁僵，就出嚟打返個圓場。<br />\n<br />\n我點都估唔到原來一個外表滿分又咁溫柔嘅女人會有咁惡嘅一面。<br />\n<br />\n過咗成日，都冇人add過我入所謂嘅班群。當我以為又俾人遺忘嘅時候，我收到兩個由陌生電話send嚟嘅WhatsApp。<br />\n<br />\n第一個：「聽日放學你有冇時間？不如一齊睇戲？」<br />\n<br />\n第二個：「小心陳浚軒。」<br />\n<br />\n我當其時成個腦都係黑人問號，因為兩個號碼嘅主人都冇同我講佢地係邊個，所以我兩個都覆咗一句「你邊位？」"},{"pid":"be57b3fb387ae5cdc64b6a0afef6394520a17da7","tid":1992752,"uid":83440,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T00:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696de26ba2454d635e89f201d7698e72c8e2affb","tid":1992752,"uid":327732,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:40:53.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82663ceeb916c7536dc40734f9dca529aa50e8aa","tid":1992752,"uid":302976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4673d46ed9705471c8030c9ea090c6ecacc0742","tid":1992752,"uid":308341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T07:21:08.000Z","msg":"女神降臨？"},{"pid":"584a4c49eb89267fbc9aee64704c5463a073a776","tid":1992752,"uid":202541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4673d46ed9705471c8030c9ea090c6ecacc0742","tid":1992752,"uid":308341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T07:21:08.000Z","msg":"女神降臨？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"睇落去咪知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6b4ab7e89cae1fd8a1d112f0713449b1c60fac","tid":1992752,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"584a4c49eb89267fbc9aee64704c5463a073a776","tid":1992752,"uid":202541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4673d46ed9705471c8030c9ea090c6ecacc0742","tid":1992752,"uid":308341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T07:21:08.000Z","msg":"女神降臨？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"睇落去咪知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T01:49:38.000Z","msg":"好耐冇更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037776e975baceabee0361f9408479bb4b5a0a07","tid":1992752,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:32:53.000Z","msg":"文呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708bc757489c17dd33ffb42cb5382b01290df464","tid":1992752,"uid":176169,"like":2,"dislike"